public abstract class AbstractRuleObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements RuleObjectInterface

Defines the RuleObject and provides basic methods for RuleObject processing. The executeRule() method is user-defined.

1.0
Author:

public abstract java.lang.Boolean executeRule()

Executes the rule defined in the object. Must return a Boolean value. Rules are evaluated such that "true" means that conformance has occurred.
